{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbb091f818","title":"关于日本、南京情况及我们的建议致张学良电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3fc822ab9f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":14,"articleId":"bbb091f818"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c5a308a0ba","type":"paragraph","text":"关于日本、南京情况及我们的建议","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"dc2d154bb3","type":"paragraph","text":"致张学良电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"a7b7c411ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月14日）李宜兄：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"c49ca14dec","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、情况：（一）日本三相会议，认文变为革命的，准备支持南京（二）南京甚悦乱，恐事变扩大，急下免职令，军队交军委直辖（三）何应钦到郑州，判断专为指挥进攻。（四）樊军向演关，方=守咸阳。乙、建议：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"23b284bc06","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）闻冯钦哉师集中西安，冯不可靠，希注意，宜以孙师集中西安、渔关间。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"6151923571","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）胡、毛、曾、关甚恐忧，日内尚无可为，主要注意樊、万。（三）东北军愈集结愈好，但兰州万不可失（四）红军准备全力增援。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"b98f990c91","type":"paragraph","text":"弟东来","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"},{"id":"dc50f5f54e","type":"paragraph","text":"寒子1]指樊崧甫。[2]指万耀煌。[3]指胡宗南、毛炳文、曾万钟、关麟征。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818"}],"page":{"id":"0d3d4c0b59","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"bbb091f818","start":163,"end":163}}}},"__N_SSG":true}